{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 5.1 Follower that pans audio to follow Phantom Center position from SBP Surround Scope. Includes coordinate transformation (offset, scale, invert) and pseudo-acoustic filtering based on angle difference. Link slider1/2 to SurroundScope slider24/25 via Parameter Modulation.\par}
}

