{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 \outlinelevel0 \b \fs36 SBP ReaSciFi\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 Modular sci-fi UI sound generator for REAPER.\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 Features in this initial implementation:\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa0 \li360 \fi-360 \bullet \tx360\tab Dedicated JSFX preview engine for one-shot and drone design.\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa0 \li360 \fi-360 \bullet \tx360\tab Macro workflow for UI beeps, clicks, glitches, drones, and telemetry textures.\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa0 \li360 \fi-360 \bullet \tx360\tab Timbre and Motion XY pads.\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa0 \li360 \fi-360 \bullet \tx360\tab Built-in LFO and MSEG-style modulation controls.\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa0 \li360 \fi-360 \bullet \tx360\tab Factory preset families oriented toward interface sound design.\sa180\par}
